Featured Photographer: @mikha_elroy
About the Shot:
I like to take #timelapse with my #gopro , but I hadn't tried to take night lapse. Last night I wanted to try the #nightlapse mode. I took this night lapse from my home at #Bandung , #Indonesia .
How the Shot was Captured:
I took this shot on my #Hero4Silver, set it up on the wood with a tape to make it stable, using the GoPro app to control the setting on my camera. I used the night lapse mode. The settings were - 30 Sec | Continuous | 12 MP / Wide | 5500K | GoPro Color | ISO 100 | High Sharpness. I edited it with GoPro Studio which automatically changed it from 4:3 to 16:9 ratio.
